@NODE "Miscellaneous" "Miscellaneous"

 Miscellaneous
 -------------

 * You can add your own pictures simply copying them into 'pics' directory.
   Picture name must exactly match person's e-mail address. Included pictures
   are 65x65 in size just because they fit nicely into Thor's main window
   (font size 13).

 * Each time an unknown address is encoutered picture named 'joe_user' is
   displayed. You must not rename or delete this file.

 * 'Odin' creates temporary file in 'T:' directory. It is wise to keep 'T:'
   in 'Ram Disk:' to prevent unnecessary disk activity.

 * It is rather not recommended to iconify Thor when Odin is running.
   In case of emergency you can quit Odin typing rx "address ODIN;QUIT" in
   shell.

 * I'd like to thank Leon Woestenberg and Marco Talamelli. Looking into
   their sources was more than inspiring ;-)

@ENDNODE


